price: 78. Has he known the Unseen or has he taken a covenant from the Most Gracious (Allâh)?
arabic: أَطَّلَعَ ٱلۡغَيۡبَ أَمِ ٱتَّخَذَ عِندَ ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنِ عَهۡدٗا
